    <p>Cumulative Ordinal Encoding</p>
    <p>I ordinals &lt;k as vectors v in Nk:</p>
    <p>(v) = k1 v[k 1] + +0 v[0]</p>
    <p>I ordinals &lt; k</p>
    <p>as vector sequences V = v1 vp:</p>
    <p>(V) = (v1) + +(vp)</p>
    <p>I ordinals &lt;k as #-separated vector sequences x = V1#V2##Vm# (aka codes):</p>
    <p>(x) = (V1Vm) +(V1Vm1) + +(V1)</p>
